    <title>hexo_guide</title>
    <link href="/2024/07/19/hexo-guide/"/>
    <url>/2024/07/19/hexo-guide/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>1、安装node.js<br>2、安装git</p><figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs stylus">设置<br>git config <span class="hljs-attr">--global</span> user<span class="hljs-selector-class">.name</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;你的git用户名&quot;</span><br>git config <span class="hljs-attr">--global</span> user<span class="hljs-selector-class">.email</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;你的git登录邮箱&quot;</span><br>检查<br>git config user<span class="hljs-selector-class">.name</span><br>git config user<span class="hljs-selector-class">.email</span><br>创建ssh,并配置到github<br>ssh-keygen -t rsa -C <span class="hljs-string">&quot;youremail&quot;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>3、安装hexo</p><figure class="highlight cmake"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cmake">npm <span class="hljs-keyword">install</span> -g hexo-cli<br>hexo init myblog<br>cd myblog <br>npm <span class="hljs-keyword">install</span><br><br>hexo g<br>hexo server<br><br>访问localhost:<span class="hljs-number">4000</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>参考：<br><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/cat_bayi/article/details/128725230">https://blog.csdn.net/cat_bayi/article/details/128725230</a><br><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/sinat_37781304/article/details/82729029">https://blog.csdn.net/sinat_37781304/article/details/82729029</a></p>]]></content>
    
    
    
